OL,3,CResidents concerned after future of
OL,4,CJersey Cheshire Home 'in doubt'
OL,6,FThe only residential facility in
OL,7,FJersey caring for adults with
OL,8,Fdisabilities says the future of the
OL,9,Fservice is 'in doubt' due to financial
OL,10,Fshortages.
OL,12,FJersey Cheshire Home looks after those
OL,13,Fwho can no longer live in their own
OL,14,Fhome, offering specialist care and
OL,15,Frehabilitation.
OL,17,FHowever, Deputy Inna Gardier has now
OL,18,Fwarned that if the charity is unable
OL,19,Fto sustain its current level of care,
OL,20,Fit could lead to more pressure on
OL,21,Fgovernment health services.
