OL,3,CResidents concerned after future of
OL,4,CJersey Cheshire Home 'in doubt'
OL,6,FResident Stanley Baudains says the
OL,7,Fcare is life-changing, he says: "It
OL,8,Fwas like someone put a light on in my
OL,9,Flife, it was just such a vast
OL,10,Fincredible difference from day one,
OL,11,Fabsolutely amazing."
OL,13,FHe adds: "It means the earth, we have
OL,14,Fa vast amount of independence and
OL,15,Fwonderful surroundings.
