OL,3,CResidents concerned after future of
OL,4,CJersey Cheshire Home 'in doubt'
OL,6,F"Good care, nurses on duty twenty-four
OL,7,Fseven, lots of things to do. None of
OL,8,Fus would want to be here by choice,
OL,9,Fbut this is where we are and this is a
OL,10,Funique home and we are lucky to be
OL,11,Fhere."
OL,13,FThe charity has been offering support
OL,14,Fand rehabilitation to its 31 residents
OL,15,Ffor over 40 years.
OL,17,FIt costs #3.5 million a year to
OL,18,Foperate the centre which offers
OL,19,Fspecialist services like hydrotherapy
OL,20,Fand physio.
