OL,3,CResidents concerned after future of
OL,4,CJersey Cheshire Home 'in doubt'
OL,6,F"I mean that is what we are about and
OL,7,Fthat is what our motive is about, it
OL,8,Fis not to make money- we are a charity
OL,9,Fand we are trying to do the best we
OL,10,Fpossibly can for the individuals in
OL,11,Four care."
OL,13,FJersey Cheshire Home is the only
OL,14,Fservice on the island offering this
OL,15,Flevel of care to adults living with
OL,16,Fdisabilities, and its closure would
OL,17,Fsee more financial pressure put on
OL,18,Fhealth services.
