OL,3,CResidents concerned after future of
OL,4,CJersey Cheshire Home 'in doubt'
OL,6,FResident Valerie Cleaton, says the
OL,7,Fcharity is special to her, she
OL,8,Fexplains: "It is a place that should
OL,9,Fkeep going, it will leave a lot of
OL,10,Fpeople like me who have no family
OL,11,Falone- this is what we call home."
OL,13,FDeputy for St Helier North Inna
OL,14,FGardiner has proposed an amendment to
OL,15,FJersey's Government budget, which will
OL,16,Fbe announced the week starting Monday
OL,17,F25 November.
