OL,6,FIf the funding is not supplied, staff
OL,7,Fmembers, hydrotherapy facilities and
OL,8,Fthe home will be unable to care for
OL,9,Fthose with the highest needs meaning
OL,10,Fmore pressure will be put on health
OL,11,Fservices.
OL,13,FJim says whatever happens next week he
OL,14,Fis hopeful discussions can continue
OL,15,Ffor them to receive financial support
OL,16,Fto protect its future, most
OL,17,Fimportantly for the residents who need
OL,18,Fit so much.
